OL,3,C'Close to life support': hospitality
OL,4,Cbusinesses urgent plea for help
OL,6,FThe cost of produce is pushing many
OL,7,Fbusinesses to the limit, with some
OL,8,Fproducts costing three-times the price
OL,9,Fthey were the previous year.
OL,11,FVAT rates remain at 20% for
OL,12,Fhospitality businesses - those within
OL,13,Fthe industry want to see it halved.
OL,15,FAnd rising energy costs are also
OL,16,Fplaying their part, along with a rise
OL,17,Fin the minimum wage and the cost of
OL,18,Fliving crisis.
