OL,3,C'Close to life support': hospitality
OL,4,Cbusinesses urgent plea for help
OL,6,F"This is the toughest year we've ever
OL,7,Fexperienced," he says. "Tougher than
OL,8,Fthe last financial crash, the post-
OL,9,FBrexit impact and even the Covid-19
OL,10,FLockdown.
OL,12,F"Three years ago, we were paying
OL,13,Faround #19 for five litres of olive
OL,14,Foil. Now, it costs around #57.
OL,16,F"It is a calamity of cost increases.
OL,17,FWe have just had a record year for
OL,18,Fturnover for 2023, around #2.8 million
OL,19,Fbut we didn't make a penny - we
OL,20,Factually lost slightly last year.
