OL,4,Cbusinesses urgent plea for help
OL,6,F"We are getting close to life support,
OL,7,Fbut we're not on life support just
OL,8,Fyet."
OL,10,FPeter is managing to hang on but other
OL,11,Fbusinesses in the industry have had to
OL,12,Fcall time.
OL,14,FSoaring costs have also forced Penny
OL,15,FLynch to close her takeaway and deli,
OL,16,FA Taste of Honey in Didsbury, south
OL,17,FManchester, after trying everything
OL,18,Fshe could to save it.
