OL,6,FShe said: "I feel like I've done all
OL,7,Fmy crying now. I think my crying sort
OL,8,Fof peaked on Saturday when I closed.
OL,10,F"I sold my house and put the money in
OL,11,Fto clear debts. Then I thought we
OL,12,Fcould do a meal deal that would
OL,13,Fcompete with the supermarkets and I
OL,14,Fspent a lot of money doing that, but I
OL,15,Fcouldn't compete with those big
OL,16,Fbusinesses.
OL,18,F"I didn't expect to have to close so
OL,19,Fsoon but it did just get to a point
OL,20,Fwhere I needed to stop."
