OL,6,FIt is not only small businesses like
OL,7,FPenny's that just cannot carry on.
OL,9,FPaul Askew owns The Art School
OL,10,Frestaurant in Liverpool and is joint
OL,11,FChair of the Royal Academy of Culinary
OL,12,FArts North.
OL,14,FHe joined Granada Reports presenters
OL,15,FLucy Meacock and Gamal Fahnbulleh in
OL,16,Fstudio to discuss issues facing the
OL,17,Fhospitality industry.
OL,19,FIn January, celebrity chef after he
OL,20,Fwas his successful restaurant in
OL,21,FManchester due to spiralling costs.
