OL,3,C'Close to life support': hospitality
OL,4,Cbusinesses urgent plea for help
OL,6,FThe chef said his job as a presenter
OL,7,Fon Channel 4's Sunday Brunch each week
OL,8,Fbrought customers through the doors.
OL,10,FHe said: "If Greens is having to
OL,11,Fclose, then what are the chances for
OL,12,Fmany other small hospitality
OL,13,Fbusinesses?"
OL,15,FSimon is now calling for a VAT break,
OL,16,Ftelling Good Morning Britain: "A VAT
OL,17,Fcut would really help, paying VAT on
OL,18,Ffood and VAT on employee wages...it's
OL,19,Fa lot."
