OL,3,C'Close to life support': hospitality
OL,4,Cbusinesses urgent plea for help
OL,6,FIt is a move Masterchef winner and
OL,7,Fowner of Wood restaurant in
OL,8,FManchester, Simon Wood, agrees would
OL,9,Fhelp. He says that 20% VAT is
OL,10,Fcrippling some hospitality businesses:
OL,12,F"26 countries in Europe are on a lower
OL,13,FVAT rate than we are," he said. "We're
OL,14,Fasking for a decrease to 10% or 12%,
OL,15,Fjust to give us a chance.
OL,17,F"It's not a handout - we're just
OL,18,Fasking for a little bit of respite
OL,19,Fwhile we find ourselves in a situation
OL,20,Fthat we just can't control."
