OL,6,FHe also runs The White Horse pub in
OL,7,FChurton near Chester, which was
OL,8,Frecently named in the top 100
OL,9,FGastropubs in the UK.
OL,11,FHe said: "We have the same problem if
OL,12,Fwe are busy or quiet because the costs
OL,13,Fare too high around what we do.
OL,15,F"It's not about people coming, it's
OL,16,Fabout the costs around us not matching
OL,17,Fup."
OL,19,F"It is important to keep talking about
OL,20,Fthe issues we are facing.
